Package mapred

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JobTrackerInterface
    This class is a interface of JobTracker which is a remote object
    Mapper
    This class is a interface of programmer's Mapper
    Reducer
    This class is a interface of Reducer
    TaskTrackerInterface
    This is a interface class of Task Tracker
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JobClient
    This class is designed to provide the user to initiate a job and monitor the job's status.
    JobConfiguration
    This class is a bean which was used to record the necessary parameters for running the map reduce job.
    JobScheduler
    This class is used to help the JobTracker to schedule the nodes for different functions.
    JobTracker
    This class has to be deployed on the master node.
    MapRunner
    This class is used to start a thread to run the distributed mapper work
    Merger
    This class is used to merge all the contents of the partitions from different nodes into one
    Partitioner
    1.
    ReduceRunner
    This class is a thread to run the Reducer work
    RMIServiceInfo
    This class is used to reserve the RMI related info including dataNode's Registry port, service name, partition numbers, partition file path, taskNode's registry port and service name.
    TaskInfo  
    TaskStatusInfo
    This class is designed to encapsulate information of task status of one slave node.
    TaskThread
    This class is a thread to connect to the specific task node and handling some failures.
    TaskTracker
    This class is used to initialize the Task Tracker which was used to monitor the tasks running on the node and communicate with the JobTracker server.
